text: Pine Valley, Utah may refer to three places in Utah: *Pine Valley, Washington County, Utah, an unincorporated community *Pine Valley (Provo River), a valley along the North Fork of the Provo River in Summit and Wasatch counties in north or north-central Utah *Pine Valley (Millard County, Utah), a 50-mile (80 km) long valley in southwestern Utah, in Beaver, Millard, and Iron counties ==See also== *Pine Valley (disambiguation)
title: Pine Valley, Utah
